ces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e49c99c03ba3dfff11c2d7abf97dc3a24917297","tid":1728233,"uid":81698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T02:57:34.000Z","msg":"岩岩check過like都無like<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c46aef495a1052ff2ed63b0cea06b8536afcd5","tid":1728233,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:38:10.000Z","msg":"<strong>他們在打的是「中共政權保衛戰」，而你們僅僅是在打「香港生活方式保衛戰」</strong><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（一） Be Water(水聚散) 不能變為Be Castle（碉堡戰、陣地戰）</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">對付Be Water，<strong>第一就是分化</strong>，<strong>把勇武派、和理非派拆分</strong>，<strong>第二步是下餌，引誘勇武派進入「必守的陣地」</strong>，刺激他們建立碉堡，最好所有的勇武派都集中進入少數陣地（例如四所大學），然後<strong>隔絕、撒網、一舉成擒</strong>。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（二） 從「誰才是暴徒」辯論陷阱脫身</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">港人對抗港府還算旗鼓相當，畢竟兩邊都是被法治洗禮過的香港人，<strong>但是港人對付中共的無底綫宣傳統戰技能</strong>，坦白說，<strong>還是太嫩</strong>。世人關心香港事態的焦點從「港人要自由、要自治」，變成「人民和政府誰才是暴力方」的辯論，這正是<strong>北京</strong>要製造的<strong>焦點轉移</strong>。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（三） 一切回歸三個字 &ndash; 真普選</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">核心訴求只有一個：真普選，一切口號、行動、宣傳，都環繞真普選這單一訴求展開，<strong>這樣，世界聽得懂，連中國內地人民都聽得懂</strong>。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"9b4abda67c56ee54f53d4fc1cbb25f0dabf27558","tid":1728233,"uid":41087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:48:40.000Z","msg":"Who?"},{"pid":"f47aed50812ed0521a728b838112f260f813025f","tid":1728233,"uid":117947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:49:19.000Z","msg":"琴日un左"},{"pid":"97505d586811e0b5bb393d469d26fadabe5c5776","tid":1728233,"uid":30029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:03:34.000Z","msg":"仲衰過達哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e78e55cd3ff18d602a8078b60a601966b29e4f","tid":1728233,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:25:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd2714a17dee376ac3905643a010408dfa00ddd8","tid":1728233,"uid":26563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:25:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sjXM8by.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsjXM8by.jpg&h=6a190771&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52577e52bc2be243450e092dc4fa205bedec10af","tid":1728233,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:27:07.000Z","msg":"睇開扑縮"}]}